    {
      "type": "text", "id": "p_agent_components",
      "x": 592, "y": 348, "width": 320, "height": 130,
      "text": "AgentSession components:\n  STT:  Deepgram nova-2\n  TTS:  Google Cloud (de-DE)\n  LLM:  not used (relay only)\n\nAutomatic publishers (signals.py):\n  AutoGreeter        once on first persona\n  HeartbeatPublisher every 30s\n  BackchannelWatcher \"mhm\" if user 6s+",
      "originalText": "AgentSession components:\n  STT:  Deepgram nova-2\n  TTS:  Google Cloud (de-DE)\n  LLM:  not used (relay only)\n\nAutomatic publishers (signals.py):\n  AutoGreeter        once on first persona\n  HeartbeatPublisher every 30s\n  BackchannelWatcher \"mhm\" if user 6s+",
      "fontSize": 11, "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#374151", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
